B

BasicFlight - Class in entities
A basic flight class with a unique number, a capacity, seats to store Bookings of passengers, and a width that specifies the number of seats per row.
BasicFlight(int, int, int) - Constructor for class entities.BasicFlight
Initialize the flight with the specified number, width and capacity.
bookFirstClassPassenger() - Method in class startup.FlightReservationSystem
Read the name for a passenger, the number for a flight, the seat for the passenger, and the meal plan for the passenger, and then book the passenger on the flight as a first class passenger.
Booking - Class in entities
This is the class to record the information for a Person booking a BasicFlight.
Booking(Person, BasicFlight) - Constructor for class entities.Booking
Initialize the Booking with the prescribed Person and flight.
bookPassenger() - Method in class startup.FlightReservationSystem
Read the name for a passenger, the number for a flight, and then book the passenger on the flight as a regular passenger.
BookPassengerCommand - Class in commands
A class which handles the booking of a passenger on a flight.
BookPassengerCommand() - Constructor for class commands.BookPassengerCommand
